| Method                       | Params                                             | Ret                            | Note |
|------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+------|
| <<method to config GL>>      |                                                    |                                |      |
|------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+------|
| glEnable/glDisable           | GL.GL_DEPTH_TEST                                   |                                |      |
|------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+------|
| glHint                       | target:int, mode:int                               |                                |      |
|------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+------|
| glClear                      | GL.GL_COLOR_BUFFER_BIT                             |                                |      |
|                              | .GL_DEPTH_BUFFER_BIT                               |                                |      |
|------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+------|
| glViewPort                   | start,end,width,height:int                         |                                |      |
|------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+------|
| glMatrixMode                 | enum                                               |                                |      |
|                              | GL.GL_PROJECTION                                   |                                |      |
|                              | .GL_MODElVIEW                                      |                                |      |
|------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+------|
| glLoadIdentity               |                                                    |                                |      |
|------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+------|
| glFrustumf                   | left,right,btm,top:float                           |                                |      |
|                              | near,far:float                                     |                                |      |
|------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+------|
| glShadeMode                  | mode:int                                           |                                |      |
|------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+------|
| glEnableClientState          | GL.GL_VERTEX_APPLY : enable vertex location buffer |                                |      |
|                              | .GL_COLOR_ARRAy : enable vertex color buffer       |                                |      |
|------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+------|
| glFinish                     |                                                    | To end draw                    |      |
|------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+------|
| glDisableClientState         | int                                                | release Bufffer and disable GL |      |
|------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+------|
| <<method to draw GL buffer>> |                                                    |                                |      |
|------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+------|
| glClearColor                 | red, green,blue,alpha:float                        |                                |      |
|------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+------|
| glDrawArrays                 | mode                                               |                                |      |
|                              | first : first index of vertex in  Buffer           |                                |      |
|                              | count:int : size of all vertex to draw             |                                |      |
|------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+------|
| <<method to handler data>>   |                                                    |                                |      |
|------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------+------|
| glVertexPointer              | size : entry size of single Items                  |                                |      |
|                              | type : GL.FLOAT for float, .GL_FIXED for int etc.  |                                |      |
|                              | stride:int :                                       |                                |      |
|                              | pBuf:Buffer                                        |                                |      |
